<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-2475] HTTP (Stream) to File only writes part of InputStream to File</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-2475</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The follwoing route only writes part of the http input stream to the file output (always&lt;br/&gt;
in chunks of 1,2,4 or 8KB).:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;               &amp;lt;route id=&quot;RestToTempDir&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;from uri=&quot;jetty:&lt;a href=&quot;http://0.0.0.0:8162/muyrl&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://0.0.0.0:8162/muyrl&lt;/a&gt;&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;setHeader headerName=&quot;CamelFileExchangeFile&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                               &amp;lt;header&amp;gt;message.id&amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;/setHeader&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;to&lt;br/&gt;
                               uri=&quot;file://c:/temp/?fileName=${date:now:yyyyMMdd}/asm-${id}.xml&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;setBody&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                               &amp;lt;header&amp;gt;CamelFileExchangeFile&amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;/setBody&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are workarounds, but I would change streams to always read until EOF (if possible)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Possible workaround 1:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;convertBodyTo type=&quot;java.lang.String&quot;/&amp;gt; to force it to convert the stream to string before writing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Possible workaround 2 is to write to a queue first&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;               &amp;lt;route id=&quot;RestToTempDir&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;from uri=&quot;jetty:&lt;a href=&quot;http://0.0.0.0:8162/myurl&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://0.0.0.0:8162/myurl&lt;/a&gt;&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;inOnly uri=&quot;activemq:topic=TempTopic&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;setBody&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                               &amp;lt;header&amp;gt;message.id&amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;/setBody&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;setHeader headerName=&quot;CamelFileExchangeFile&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                               &amp;lt;header&amp;gt;message.id&amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;/setHeader&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;route id=&quot;TempAssemblyToTempArchiveDirectory&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;from uri=&quot;activemq:topic:TempTopic&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;setHeader headerName=&quot;CamelFileExchangeFile&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                               &amp;lt;header&amp;gt;message.id&amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;/setHeader&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                       &amp;lt;to&lt;br/&gt;
                               uri=&quot;file://c:/xmlarchive_noxslt/?fileName=${date:now:yyyyMMdd}/asm-${id}.xml&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
